# LapViewer Git Workflow

| Branch | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `dev` | Integration — merge verified branches here ([D-004](docs/DECISIONS.md)) |
| `master` | Deploy snapshots — promote when check + test + smoke pass ([D-025](docs/DECISIONS.md)) |

**Daily work:** branch `feature/*`, `fix/*`, or `chore/*` from `dev`; run `npm run check` (and `npm test` when relevant); merge to `dev` when complete.

**Remote:** derive before any push — `git remote -v`, `git status -sb`. Never assume remote state. Push per [D-012](docs/DECISIONS.md) when a remote exists; ask before adding one.

**Merge / promote / deploy:** use the `lapviewer-promote` skill. Deploy details: [DEPLOYMENT.md](docs/DEPLOYMENT.md).

Do not change `git config`, force-push protected branches, or commit secrets.
